an officer at your nearest branch.\\n3. **Complete the Application Form** – Provide personal details, loan amount, and purpose.\\n4. **Submit Documents** – Upload scans or bring originals if you’re at a branch.\\n5. **Approval Process** – Our team will review your application, usually within 2‑5 business days, and may contact you for any additional information.\\n6. **Disbursement** – Once approved, funds are transferred to your designated account within 24‑48 hours.\\n\\nIf you’d like to start an application now, you can click the “Apply for a Loan” button on the ATB website or download the ATB mobile app and navigate to the “Loans” section. Feel free to let us know if you need help with a specific loan type or have any other questions."\n}', additional_kwargs={}, response_metadata={}, id='lc_run--019cdeb9-e1ef-7563-ae50-2ef83587b4e8-0', tool_calls=[], invalid_tool_calls=[])]}
